that if you can hold out long enough justice will prevail today 
it didnt 
the custody fight involving the sterns rachels maternal 
grandparents and her former stepmother followed waltmans arrest 
a new jersey judge awarded full custody to the sterns last 
december but gave the grandparents and the former stepmother 
visitation rights 
the sterns complied with the order sending rachel to new jersey 
twice for visits with her relatives 
but after a florida judge approved the adoption in may gary 
stern cut off visitation claiming rachel was now his daughter and 
that it was inappropriate for a child so young to be traveling back 
and forth 
