that the visitation was causing rachel to become confused about her 
identity and her family 
last month a bridgeton judge found the sterns in contempt of 
court for adopting rachel in florida and interrupting the visits 
rachel who enters first grade this fall has been bounced from 
one family to another since her teenage mother died after a truck 
